le>   My take.</span><hr size=1> First off, yes ... Verant can track items.  Will they give the manastone back to Lovely?  There is a 99.9 % chance of not getting it back.  Will they give you a list of names on that person's account?  No, because that infringes on a person's right to privacy.  Will they give you the names of who the manastone is given / traded to?  Nope, again, that infringes on a person's rights.  <br>
<br>
If you ask me, blame doesn't lie with just one single person in this.  Equate it to this : Would you hand someone (whom you don't even know or have only known a few days) your car keys and say 'Hey, we're passing around my car keys so everyone can go to lunch!'.  If you say yes, then you deserve to have your car stolen.  <br>
<br>
The point is, if you take people along on raids that you don't know - don't pass around the manastone.  Who cares if you have to wait extra time for mana ... the dragon ain't going anywhere, they don't wander around last time I checked.  I'm not siding with Xanduron, nor am I siding with Lovely.  I think it's everyone's fault who was involved and 500 emails to VI yammering about it most likely won't help your case. <p><center><img SRC="http://inkieisme.homestead.com/files/Talendor.jpg"></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showMessage?topicID=410.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showMessage?topicID=408.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.emailToFriend?topicID=391.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.threadControl?topicID=391.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=391.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=391.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub18.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><